  "body": "`Push` should expire at a certain token, and then we can eliminate `Pop`.\r\n\r\nThe current implementation makes it too easy to pop the wrong indentation, and get output like\r\n\r\n```scala\r\n[info]   ===========\r\n[info]   => Obtained\r\n[info]   ===========\r\n[info]   {\r\n[info]     val x = 1\r\n[info]\r\n[info]     def log(split: Split): String =\r\n[info]       s\"$split\"\r\n[info]     }\r\n```"
